{"tid":1021346,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國太空總署放棄「機遇號」火星探測器 (15:04)","createTime":"2019-02-14T07:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T09:20:17.000Z","uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1de667b141b3f870f2fb068e53794f4d5762a450","tid":1021346,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"美國太空總署（NASA）宣布，放棄執行任務長達14年半的「機遇號」（Opportunity）火星探測器。<br />\n<br />\n機遇號在2004年1月24日與另一探測器「勇氣號」（Spirit）成功登陸火星展開探索之旅，「機遇號」是一架太陽能車，<span style=\"color: red;\">原本只執行90個火星日的探測任務，行駛1000米，但表現超出預期，工作14年半，行駛了45公里</span>，更發現火星過去曾有水分，可能適合居住。<br />\n<br />\nNASA稱，「機遇號」去年6月遇到嚴重的火星沙塵暴後一直失去聯絡，雖已進行逾千次恢復操作，仍然無法操作「機遇號」。而「機遇號」最後一次跟地球通訊，是在火星毅力谷（Perseverance Valley）的西部邊緣。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社/英國廣播公司）"},{"pid":"a1ba144bfe9cdf72f82b7e5a7593ea36cfca29fb","tid":1021346,"uid":161341,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"F"},{"pid":"ca70e4f5d9d5f186649426ca03cdb0cdc64e4286","tid":1021346,"uid":190540,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:53:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f58164a87be70da53f36fb9d377f5c75ad2d069c","tid":1021346,"uid":75998,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"畀火星人熔咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2e0f121ee3f59a6b89e0045c2fb572d5e01e18","tid":1021346,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"OT左十幾年人工點計先"},{"pid":"e4f7c9732a1c207f8cea329b03ce8efb70c674ea","tid":1021346,"uid":128600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"OT 咗14年，而家擴工射波比人炒埋。"},{"pid":"d57492317ca51c9143420816a9123ce8b1ae595d","tid":1021346,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1ba144bfe9cdf72f82b7e5a7593ea36cfca29fb","tid":1021346,"uid":161341,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"F"},